In the recently released lore, &#039;Forest for the Trees&#039; Kindred comes across a young squire with nothing but a sword. I don&#039;t know if he was injured or not but Kindred decides to kill him. And Lamb Laughs at what Wolf did.

Like... are they just?:
&quot;Hey Lamb, you see that guy over there&quot;
&quot;Yes, what about him&quot;
&quot;Lets kill him&quot;
&quot;Okay&quot;

Seems like they&#039;re bad spirits.

